               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_977" n="N019"/>Þat he ſikþ iſ ſone vor loue ſo fare·
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_1007" n="N020"/>Anō he of ſwoninge awok ⁊ ſpeke jmiſte
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_1036" n="N021"/>Sore he wep ⁊ ſore he ſyȝte ·
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_1073" n="N022"/>And on hiſ moder he  byſiþ·
               <lb facs="#facs_1_l_1119" n="N023"/>Dame he ſaẏde led me þar þ<hi style="vertical-align: superscript;">t</hi> mayde lyþ
